  "answer": {
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <title>编程学习教程</title>\n  <style>\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4b6cb7, #182848);\n      color: #fff;\n    }\n    header {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 1rem;\n    }\n    .nav-links {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: wrap;\n      justify-content: center;\n      gap: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .nav-link {\n      text-decoration: none;\n      color: white;\n      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;\n      border-radius: 5px;\n      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <header>\n    <h2 style=\"font-weight: bold;\">编程学习教程</h2>\n    <nav class=\"nav-links\">\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">首页</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">课程</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">资源</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" class=\"nav-link\">联系</a>\n    </nav>\n  </header>\n  <section class=\"content\">\n    <p>欢迎来到编程学习教程网站，这里有丰富的编程资源供你学习。</p>\n  </section>\n  <footer>\n    <p>© 2025 编程学习教程 - 教学用途</p>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>",
